'''Ladislav Svante Rieger''' (1916–1963){{sfn|Pecinová-Kozáková|2005|pp=191–192}} was a [[Czech Republic|Czech]] [[mathematician]] who worked in the areas of [[algebra]], [[mathematical logic]], and [[axiomatic set theory]]. He is considered to be the founder of mathematical logic in the Czech Republic and Slovakia, having begun his work around 1957.{{sfn|Pecinová-Kozáková|2005|pp=190}}{{sfn|Bukovský|1997|page=452}}

